This Webapp uses the cloud technology to create the retail inventory management system.This System will ask retailers to create their accounts by providing essential details. Retailers can access their accounts by logging into the application. Once retailers successfully log in to the application they can update their inventory details, also users will be able to add new stock by submitting essential details related to the stock. Retailers and their stock details stored in DB2. They can view details of the current inventory. The System will automatically send an email alert to the retailers if there is no stock found in their accounts (using Sendgrid).  So that they can order new stock. The main motto is to help retailers track and manage stocks related to their own products.
